Note:
Rust Parser - Recursive-descent parser building a Rust AST from tokens.

Drives the streaming rust_lexer and constructs a tree of RustASTNode records.
Covers the full grammar required by the translation pipeline:
  Items:        fn (incl async/unsafe/const, generics, where, self receivers),
                struct (named/tuple/unit), enum (unit/tuple/struct variants),
                trait (methods, assoc types/consts, supertraits), impl
                (inherent + trait-for), mod, use (incl nested/glob/as), type
                alias, const, static, union.
  Types:        path (with generic args + lifetimes), reference (&/&mut/&'a),
                raw pointer (*const/*mut), array [T;N], slice [T], tuple (T,U),
                function fn(T)->U, dyn Trait, impl Trait, Self.
  Patterns:     literal, identifier binding, wildcard _, tuple, struct, enum
                ctor, reference, mut, range, or |, rest .., @ binding.
  Statements:   let (incl let-else and type), expression statements, item stmts.
  Expressions:  literals, paths/identifiers, calls, method calls, field/tuple
                access, indexing, references &/&mut, deref *, casts (as),
                binary ops (full Rust precedence), unary, assignment + compound,
                ranges .. ..=, struct literals, array/tuple/block exprs, if /
                if-let, match, loop/while/while-let/for, closures (move), the ?
                operator, return/break/continue, macro invocations name!(...).

The AST node layout is the 104-byte RustASTNode below; rust_to_hir.runa lowers
this tree into the canonical hir.runa create_hir_node IR consumed by hir_to_rust.

Dependencies:
- rust_lexer.runa
- compiler/frontend/primitives/memory/layout.runa
- compiler/frontend/primitives/core/string_core.runa
- compiler/frontend/primitives/collections/list.runa
:End Note

Import "compiler/middle/gungnir/hir/translation/frontends/rust/rust_lexer.runa" as Lexer
Import "compiler/frontend/primitives/memory/layout.runa" as Layout
Import "compiler/frontend/primitives/core/string_core.runa" as StringCore
Import "compiler/frontend/primitives/collections/list.runa" as List

